trans-unit.target: Expande o comportamento do momento da conceção para o <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> Web controlo de servidor.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner"></xref> control and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Liberta os recursos não geridos que são utilizados pelo <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner"> </xref> controlar e opcionalmente liberta os recursos geridos.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: É possível chamar Dispose quando tiver terminado de utilizar a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>classe.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O método de Dispose deixa o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>num Estado não utilizável.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar Dispose, tem de libertar todas as referências para o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>para que o recoletor de lixo pode reclame a memória que a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>foi occupying.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [recursos não geridos limpeza](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método eliminar](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada eliminar antes de libertar a última referência <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está a utilizar não irão ser libertados até que as chamadas de recoletor de lixo a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>do objeto `Finalize` método.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: O método de Dispose é chamado pelo público `Dispose()` método e o <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>método.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with `disposing` set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: O `Dispose()` invoca protegida `Dispose(Boolean)` método com `disposing` definido como `true`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>invoca `Dispose` com `disposing` definido como `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When `disposing` is `true`, the Dispose method releases all resources that are held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> references.
trans-unit.target: Quando `disposing` é `true`, o método de Dispose versões todos os recursos que são detidos por quaisquer objetos geridos que este <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>referências.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: O método de Dispose invoca o `Dispose()` método de cada objeto referenciado.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Para libertar recursos geridos e; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> para libertar recursos apenas não geridos.
